cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper is about neural network compression, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on filter-level pruning, which is a technique used in deep learning (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The regularization terms added to the importance also suggest a potential connection to data science (cs.DS).
